{"tid":1525272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發左個夢香港最靚既野係人","createTime":"2019-08-31T21:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T21:36:31.000Z","uid":289041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c86e50e3bf503bb0509edbc1de1b32a627232c7d","tid":1525272,"uid":289041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:21:15.000Z","msg":"今日發左個夢係維園同朋友分道揚鑣之後，打算Join另一班朋友...其間得番自己一個人係維園入口。過程中有不少人問我啲隊友去左邊點解我得一個人❨因為朋友都唔會上前線所以先行撤退❩ 我答佢：『佢地走晒啦...但我想留左多陣。 』 手足們都會叮囑我小心啲。<br />\n<br />\n之後重有手足想俾頭盔我，不過我知其他前線巴打比我更加需要佢所以無拎到。 當我都撤退番到安全啲既地鐵站果陣，遇到一對同路人既情侶佢地提醒我地鐵站有狗，小心啲。最後大家向唔同出口離開道別<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n番到屋企果一刻我真係好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足之間素未謀面但都會好熱心咁守望相助。 香港人... 真係唔可以輸..."},{"pid":"8e7aa54798e32bfa31fee248057446a27527a9cd","tid":1525272,"uid":25857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:23:23.000Z","msg":"屌我都試過唔止一次有手足見我自己一個俾gear我問我一唔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次都好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcf2e4409b1c6a5a8af0708da59c583d8e7c35f","tid":1525272,"uid":289041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7aa54798e32bfa31fee248057446a27527a9cd","tid":1525272,"uid":25857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:23:23.000Z","msg":"屌我都試過唔止一次有手足見我自己一個俾gear我問我一唔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次都好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:28:34.000Z","msg":"我依家每次回想起 個鼻頭都會好酸。"},{"pid":"c1d9f0e532affb7dd7e9b6c3483ee2b97d